description: BBQ with real Colorado flavor is on its way to a curb near you, with Rocky Mountain BBQ! This is real Texas-style BBQ in the heart of Colorado, made with the full flavor and amazing quality you'll find in the Lone Star state. With their wide selection of BBQ dishes and a selection of treats to satisfy your sweet tooth, Rocky Mountain BBQ is the perfect food truck for all your cravings!
name: Rocky Mountain BBQ
